<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to IGIT(MCA) - Account Created Successfully</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f3f3;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #016A70, #FFD700);
            padding: 25px;
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 140px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 22px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background: #016A70;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(1, 106, 112, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #014f53;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(1, 106, 112, 0.4);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #016A70;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Company Logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= companyLogo %>" alt="BatoiBhai Logo">
            <h1>Welcome to IGIT(MCA) App!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>We are excited to welcome you! Your account has been successfully created on <strong>IGIT(MCA)</strong> App.</p>
            <p>Get ready to discover breathtaking campsites, book outdoor adventures, and create unforgettable memories.</p>
            <p>Click the button below to log in and start your journey:</p>
            <!-- <a href="<%= loginLink %>" class="btn">Login to Your Account</a> -->
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Reach us at <a href="mailto:support@batoibhai.com">support.igitmca@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; <%= year %> IGIT(MCA). All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
